OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fto start but some low cloud in the
OL,7,Fwest and north later. Elsewhere areas
OL,8,Fof fog forming through the early
OL,9,Fhours, perhaps extensive in the south.
OL,10,FRemaining relatively mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEarly fog clearing, then
OL,13,Fdry and very mild with warm sunny
OL,14,Fspells during Wednesday. Winds slowly
OL,15,Fease throughout the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
