OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FBreezy with rain or showers Thursday.
OL,7,FLikely wet and windy at first Friday,
OL,8,Fthen cooler with showers. Saturday
OL,9,Fstarts off settled before rain arrives
OL,10,Fduring the afternoon.
